Smoky BBQ Pulled Pork Burrito

$12.99
850 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BurritoPulled PorkBBQComfort Food

Description

A smoky and savory pulled pork burrito wrapped in a warm tortilla, topped with zesty salsa and creamy sour cream.

Ingredients

  • Pulled Pork: 2 cups
  • Flour Tortilla: 2 large
  • BBQ Sauce: 1/2 cup
  • Black Beans: 1 cup
  • Corn: 1 cup
  • Shredded Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup
  • Sour Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Salsa: 1/2 cup
  • Lettuce: 1 cup
  • Avocado: 1
  • Olive Oil: 1 tbsp
